replies.body:
Just wanted to say I really respect riot for the way they handle these things. I've played for 7 years and have always diligently reported people acting that way, and it's because I know riot cares/acts on the reports.

Thank you OP for doing the right thing and thank you Riot for handling the toxic aspects of the community in such a mature and helpful way! Mad props! :)

